Why Reconciliation is Fast 🚀
👉 React reconciliation compares the previous and new virtual DOM using a diffing algorithm and updates only the changed parts in the real DOM for better performance.

Uses Virtual DOM
Uses Diffing Algorithm (O(n))
Updates only what is needed

